      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Great Northern summer\nrates from various parts Of Mon\ntana and Washington to Spokane\nwent into effect yesterday and will\ncontinue until September so with a\nreturn limit good until October 81.\nThe round trip rates are:\n\n\nSpokane to Lake Mcdonald, Bel\nton Mont, $11.30.\n\n\nSpokane to Whitefish, Mont,\n5000.\n\n\nSpokane to Chelan Falls, Wash,\ns1S.\n\n\nSpokane to Hot Springs, Madi-\nson. Wash, 50.\n\n\nSpokane to Priest Lake, Idaho,\n80 days limit, $5.15.\n\n\nSpokane to Lake Chelan. Stehe-\nkin. Wash, $15.35.\n\n\nSpokane to New port, Wash,\nweek end Saturday and Sunday,\n$3.50; Sunday. 81."
    }
  ]
